# Format After Changes

After finishing edits to files in `src/`, run:

```bash
bun run format
```

This formats all `src/**/*.{svelte,ts,js,css,html}` files with Prettier and the Svelte plugin. Run it once at the end of a set of changes, not after every individual file edit.
